The subject allows a student to take courses in accordance with his or her personal study and development plans at a foreign university for a chosen semester.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The aim of the course is to give the student the opportunity to take courses in a foreign university in accordance with his or her personal study and development plan and to gain experience in coping in a multicultural environment.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  Student: 1. has experience in working in a multicultural environment; 2. can communicate with people from other cultures; 3. has acquired vocabulary in a specific field in a foreign language environment.
